## Monitor And Logging

### Logs

- Appropriate log levels: `ERROR`, `WARN`, `INFO`, `DEBUG`
- Include relevant context
- Consistent format
- Timestamp in UTC

### Metrics

- Response Time
- Resource usage
- Error rate
- Availability

## Performance

### Optimization

- Profile before optimizing
- Document bachmarks
- Monitor Key metrics
- Premature optimization is the root of all evil

### Cache

- Define cache policies
- Document TTL
- Monitor hit/miss ratio

